title: Ed Bolian
description:
Ed Bolian is the creator of VinWiki YouTube channel, VinWIKI app, and a former record-holder of the transcontinental driving record.

 

Watch VinWiki here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCefl-5pmhZmljwZTE2KrcdA
